title: Kim Kardashian West Joins Andy For His Final Haunted House
author: TheEllenShow
description:
It's the reason for the season — Executive Producer Andy is going through a haunted house for one last time. This year, he was joined by Kim Kardashian West at Universal Studios Halloween Horror Nights for some spooktacular memories and hilarious scares!
